title: (Mon Full) Bobby Got a Bone Cut Out of His Mouth + Bobby Feud: Food You Ate the Most in Your 20’s + What’s the Haps: Eddie Messed Up As A Parent
itunes:title: (Mon Full) Bobby Got a Bone Cut Out of His Mouth + Bobby Feud: Food You Ate the Most in Your 20’s + What’s the Haps: Eddie Messed Up As A Parent
description:
Bobby recaps his surgery where he had to get bone shaved down inside of his mouth. Inside the Bobby Feud, can you name the top foods we ate the most in our 20s?  We get caught up on everyone’s weekend inside What’s the Haps! Bobby went to an amazing concert and now has a new best-seller!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
